{"trainType":"主修","grade":"2023","education":{"id":2,"nameZh":"本科"},"studentType":{"id":4,"nameZh":"普通"},"department":{"id":91,"code":"208","nameZh":"地球和空间科学学院"},"major":{"id":29,"code":"07102","nameZh":"大气科学"},"majorDirection":null,"requiredCredits":166,"awardDegree":true,"beginSemester":"2023年秋季学期","directionGen":true,"moduleTree":[{"self":{"id":43803,"parent":43802,"type":"通修课程","typeEn":"General Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":12,"requiredCredits":0,"requiredCourseNum":0,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":false,"children":[{"self":{"id":43804,"parent":43803,"type":"计算机通修","typeEn":"Computer-General","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":"分级考试进入相应班级","requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":4,"requiredCourseNum":0,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":100,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":null,"experimentPeriods":40,"periodsPerWeek":4,"course":{"id":9017,"code":"CS1001A","nameZh":"计算机程序设计A","nameEn":"Computer Programming A","totalPeriods":100,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":4,"introduction":"<p>本课程以C语言为载体，以培养计算思维和程序设计能力为目标，通过丰富而实用的示例，展示在程序设计过程中如何分析问题、组织数据并解决问题，阐述了在计算应用过程中将算法与编码相联系的具体程序设计过程，以及结构化、模块化程序设计的思想与方法。课程主要内容包括计算机基础、常用语法元素的概念及示例、基本语法与结构化程序设计、模块化程序设计与常用算法和库函数、C语言特有元素与应用示例、程序设计与计算思维深入以及附录。本课程具有两大特色，其一是快速入门，用两章内容使学生从零基础到具备解决简单问题的编程能力，避免因前期枯燥冗长的语法学习而失去对课程的兴趣；其二是侧重能力的培养，不再穷究语法细节，而是引导学生通过自主学习掌握使用计算思维分析和解决问题的方法与技巧，最终得到能力的提升而非简单的知识积累。</p>","courseGradation":"通修","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["1秋"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":93,"code":"210","nameZh":"信息科学技术学院"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":true},{"self":{"id":43815,"parent":43803,"type":"劳动教育","typeEn":"Labor Education","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":1,"requiredCourseNum":1,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit